{"tid":204301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《蘋果日報》調查組報料專線等你報料！","createTime":"2017-04-17T02:38:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T04:46:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ee861ef2818aa1905b76cb4bd5d5273dc1a2faec","tid":204301,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T02:38:51.000Z","msg":"《蘋果日報》調查組報料專線等你報料！ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170203/large/1486133099_adcc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170203%2Flarge%2F1486133099_adcc.jpg&h=5b5e3151&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《蘋果日報》多年來毋懼政治打壓，堅持揭露真相，在喉舌張牙舞爪、流言漫天亂舞的時代，《蘋果》調查組抽絲剝繭，深入追查，把陳茂波囤地、區選種票、國力博士工廠等權貴醜聞一一展現讀者眼前；結合文字、相片、動新聞，把真相全方位帶入尋常百姓家。背後支持我們的，正正是挺身而出揭露不平事的香港人，若你手中有涉及公眾利益、權貴濫權等資料，請以WhatsApp、Line、Telegram或電郵方式聯絡《蘋果》調查組，本報將有專人處理及跟進，內容絕對保密。<br />\n<br />\nWhatsApp / Line / Telegram：6829 6520<br />\n電郵： investigation@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170417&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=56259269\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170417%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D56259269&d=qJ6fIGaH6M%2FMetNSomypDwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=54e753b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170417%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D56259269&h=823ec2c6\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170417&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=56259269</a>"},{"pid":"7fec3a8c6489cc8e1379678f13089ca26182d0bd","tid":204301,"uid":63462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T03:17:25.000Z","msg":"樓主返奴工假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43b2276fa21d4ed2103f1612eeecb6fa13c88d81","tid":204301,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T03:22:12.000Z","msg":"樓主係記者?"},{"pid":"71b368ee645e7